f6_assessments.q1:
Unfortunately the budget, the timeline and the previous experience of the proposer at this stage doesn't really bring too much confidence. USD 600 for 20 hours of development is quite insufficient for such a task I presume. Not to mention the "Established contact with some companies willing to use it" stage which may well take weeks to accomplish on its own.
Again - It might be advisable to do some more work on the project and present it again to be more feasible and acceptable. Possible additions are:
-establish the contacts with willing companies;
-identify the needs of those companies and what could hook them to the idea;
-involve at least one developer in the team to tackle the above and make a more realistic budget/timeline.
